These CUDA headers are vendored from the `graphgp_cuda` extension of the original
graphgp project (https://github.com/yipihey/graphgp), MIT-licensed, © Benjamin Dodge
and Philipp Frank. They contain the per-point device kernels (cov_lookup, cholesky,
refine_logdet, refine_inv). GraphGP.jl wraps them with a thin C ABI (../graphgp_capi.cu)
so the hand-written CUDA path can be called from Julia as an optional accelerator
alongside the portable KernelAbstractions kernels.
